  <text>
      <body>
         <pb n="1r" facs="lf_ratansi_arVol01Doc30.jpg"/>
         <div xml:id="orig_div1" xml:lang="ara" type="invocation" rend="top centre">
            <p>بمنّه تعالى</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div1" corresp="#orig_div1">
            <p>By the Grace of God</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div2" xml:lang="ara" type="maintext">
            <p>
               <lb/>اقر
               <persName ref="#ahmad">احمد بن سليمان بن رجب المقيمي</persName>
               ان عليه 
               <persName ref="#ratansi">للسيت رطنسيه بن
               <lb/>برسوتم البانياني</persName>
               ثمانين قرشاً فضة افرنسيسياً حقاً مؤجلاً
               <lb/>عنه الي مضي ثلاثة اشهر زمانا من يومنا قذا اقراراً منه له بذلك
               <lb/>بتاريخ
               <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">يوم
               <num>٢٣</num> 
               من شهر شوال سنة
               <num>١٣١١</num></date> 
               و كتبه الفقير 
               <persName ref="#abdullahAlBahri">عبدالله بن
               <lb/>يعوب بن يوسف البحري</persName>
               بيده
               <lb/>و بعرفاني به 
               <persName ref="#khalifa">خليف بن محمد</persName>
               و
               <persName ref="#salim">سالم بن سعيد</persName>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div2" corresp="#orig_div2">
            <p>
               <lb/><persName ref="#ahmad">Ahmad bin Sulaiman bin Rajab Al-Muqimi</persName> acknowledges that he owes to the Seth <persName ref="#ratansi">Ratansi bin
               <lb/>Pursottam Al-Banyani</persName> <measure type="currency" unit="qirsh" quantity="80">eighty silver French <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qirsh">qurush</ref></measure>, an obligation that is delayed
               <lb/>from him for three months’ time from this date, and this is an acknowledgment of that from him to him 
               <lb/>on the <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">23rd day of the month of Shawwal 1311</date>, and it was written by <persName ref="#abdullahAlBahri">Abdullah 
               <lb/>bin Yaqub bin Yusuf Al-Bahri</persName>, by his own hand
               <lb/>And it was made known to <persName ref="#khalifa">Khalifa bin Mohammed</persName> and <persName ref="#salim">Salim bin Said</persName>
            </p>
         </div>
      </body>
